<sect2 id="using-sidebar-tools">
    <title>Tools view</title>

    <para>
        The tools view from right sidebar hosts the list of actions available to process actions on selection.
        The list is an icon-view sorted by categories of tools. This view give a quick preview of all actions from main menu.
        For example, with the Image Editor, you can adjust the size of the current image with the relevant crop tool.
    </para>

    <sect3 id="using-sidebar-tools-editor">
        <title>Sidebar Tools of the Image Editor</title>
        <para>
            <inlinemediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                    <imagedata fileref="&path;using-sidebar-tools.png" format="PNG" />
                </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject>
        </para>
    </sect3>

</sect2>

